This repository contains course files for the language learning application
"Artikulate". For more information about Artikulate please visit its project
website https://projects.kde.org/projects/playground/edu/artikulate.

The provided courses are created by the people listed in file AUTHORS. You can
use, modify, and redistribute the provided files under the following terms:


Course Files:
=============
All course files contained in this repository (especially those included in
directories "skeletons" and "courses") are free; you can redistribute and or
modify them under the terms of the"Creative Commons Attribution-Share Alike 3.0
Unported" license. The license text can be found in the file COPYING.COURSES.

Directory Structure of "course":
-------------
The directory "courses" has the following structure (and scripts depend on this
structure to be correct!):
* "courses" contains a folder for each course (usually this should be associated
  to a skeleton file)
* each of these course folders contains a subfolder for each language in that
  the course exists

Example:
courses
 + basic
   + de
     + de.xml
     + < several sound files >
   + fr
     + fr.xml
      + < several sound files >

Directory Structure of "skeletons":
-------------
The directory contains course skeleton files without any further subfolders.


